# Permission Fix Plan

## Goal
Fix the issue where users with "Partner" role (who are administrators) cannot see the "Add Plan" button because the system only recognizes "Administrator" as the owner role.

## Changes

### [lib/utils/permissions.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/utils/permissions.dart)

- Add `isOwner(String role)` helper method.
- Update `roleOwner` constant to be used less directly, or keep it for reference.
- Update all permission check methods to use `isOwner(role)` instead of `role == roleOwner`.
- `isOwner` will return true if role is 'Administrator' OR 'Partner'.

